{{#if (eq event.displayName 'Wedding Breakaway')}}
    <div class="rsvp-container">
      <div class="event-details">
        <h5>You have an event update!</h5>
        <h1>{{event.displayName}}</h1>


        <div class="event-field mb48 mt48">
          <h3 class="mb8">Dear {{currentUser.firstName}},</h3>
          <p>It’s almost time to celebrate our special day with you! Here are a few details that you need to know about the big day. </p>
        </div>

        {{#if event.whatToRemember}}
          <div class="event-field highlighted">
            <h3>What to remember</h3>
            <p>{{simple-format event.whatToRemember}}</p>
          </div>
        {{/if}}


        <div class="event-field">
          <h2>The Venue</h2>
          <p>We know, we know - by now you must be bursting to know where the wedding venue is. And soon you will! Thank you for your patience thus far, and for indulging us as we attempt to create a wonderful surprise just for you.
          <br><br><b>Please select your option of choice below:</b></p>
        </div>


        <div class="big-button {{if selectedOptionA 'expanded'}}">
          <div class="event-field header" {{action 'selectOptionA'}}>
            <h3 class="mb16">Option A: The adventure seeker</h3>
            <p class="mb16">If you love the thrill of surprises and venturing into the unknown, this option is for you. Allow yourself to be guided to our venue by the directions below. All you have to do is follow these to the tee, and look out for the M&amp;C signs along the way.</p>
          </div>

          {{#if selectedOptionA}}
              <div class="event-field">
                <p class="mb16">Depending on your starting point, it can take between 2-3 hours to travel to the venue. We’ve provided estimated times for 6 major areas. We entered the area name into Google Maps (e.g. “Durbanville”) and used the traffic prediction tool on Maps for a Wednesday morning/afternoon. You can use this to plan your departure time for a 2:00pm arrival at the venue. </p>

                <ul class="text-left">
                  <li {{action (mut showDurbavilleDirections) (not showDurbavilleDirections)}}><b>Durbanville:</b> Between 1h50min and 2h10min (we recommend 2h30min just to be safe) - <i class="link">{{if showDurbavilleDirections 'hide' 'show'}} directions</i></li>
                  {{#if showDurbavilleDirections}}
                    <ul class="text-left">
                      <b>Directions</b>
                      <li>Get on N7/R45 (merge onto N7/R45 toward Moorreesburg/Vredenburg if you are coming from the R302)</li>
                      <li>Follow N7 to R393 (After approximately 62km, you will encounter a roundabout - take the second exit to stay on the N7 for another 44km).</li>
                      <li>Turn right onto the R393. After 800m, turn right again. </li>
                      <li>After another 8.4km, turn right. Your destination will be in front of you 500m later.</li>
                    </ul>
                  {{/if}}

                  <li {{action (mut showLadismithDirections) (not showLadismithDirections)}}><b>Ladismith:</b> Between 4h50min and 5h10 min (we recommend 5h30 min to be safe) - <i class="link">{{if showLadismithDirections 'hide' 'show'}} directions</i></li>
                  {{#if showLadismithDirections}}
                    <ul class="text-left">
                      <b>Directions</b>
                      <li>Head North toward R62</li>
                      <li>Turn left onto R62</li>
                      <li>After 9.2km, turn left to stay on the R62 for another 146km</li>
                      <li>At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit onto Voortrekker Ave/R60. Follow this road for approximately 47.6km</li>
                      <li>Turn right onto High St/R60</li>
                      <li>Turn left onto N1</li>
                      <li>Turn right onto Michell's Pass/R43</li>
                      <li>Turn left onto Voortrekker St</li>
                      <li>Turn left onto R46</li>
                      <li>Turn right onto R44</li>
                      <li>Continue straight onto R365</li>
                      <li>Turn right onto N7 and drive for approximately 19.5km</li>
                      <li>Turn right onto R393. After 800m, turn right again. </li>
                      <li>After another 8.4km, turn right. Your destination will be in front of you 500m later.</li>
                    </ul>
                  {{/if}}


                  <li {{action (mut showSouthernSuburbsDirections) (not showSouthernSuburbsDirections)}}><b>Southern Suburbs:</b> Between 2h10min and 2h30min (we recommend 2h45 min just to be safe) - <i class="link">{{if showSouthernSuburbsDirections 'hide' 'show'}} directions</i></li>
                  {{#if showSouthernSuburbsDirections}}
                    <ul class="text-left">
                      <b>Directions</b>
                      <li>Get on to the N1 heading to Paarl</li>
                      <li>Take exit 10 for Century City Drive/N7 toward Goodwood/Malmesbury</li>
                      <li>Keep left at the fork to continue on Exit 13A, follow signs for N7/Malmesbury and merge onto N7</li>
                      <li>Follow N7 to R393 (After approximately 62km, you will encounter a roundabout - take the second exit to stay on the N7 for another 44km).</li>
                      <li>Turn right onto the R393. After 800m, turn right again. </li>
                      <li>After another 8.4km, turn right. Your destination will be in front of you 500m later.</li>
                    </ul>
                  {{/if}}

                  <li {{action (mut showSeaPointDirections) (not showSeaPointDirections)}}><b>Sea Point/Cape Town:</b> Between 2h10 and 2h30min (we recommend 2h45min just to be safe) - <i class="link">{{if showSeaPointDirections 'hide' 'show'}} directions</i></li>
                  {{#if showSeaPointDirections}}
                    <ul class="text-left">
                      <b>Directions</b>
                      <li>Get on to Nelson Mandela Boulevard/N1/N2</li>
                      <li>Merge onto the N1, follow signs for Paarl/Bellville/R27/Milnetron</li>
                      <li>Take exit 10 for Century City Drive/N7 toward Goodwood/Malmesbury</li>
                      <li>Keep left at the fork to continue on Exit 13A, follow signs for N7/Malmesbury and merge onto N7</li>
                      <li>Follow N7 to R393 (After approximately 62km, you will encounter a roundabout - take the second exit to stay on the N7 for another 44km).</li>
                      <li>Turn right onto the R393. After 800m, turn right again. </li>
                      <li>After another 8.4km, turn right. Your destination will be in front of you 500m later.</li>
                    </ul>
                  {{/if}}

                  <li {{action (mut showSomersetDirections) (not showSomersetDirections)}}><b>Somerset West:</b> 2h10-2h50 min (we recommend 3 hours just to be safe) - <i class="link">{{if showSomersetDirections 'hide' 'show'}} directions</i></li>
