                    <ul class="text-left">
                      <b>Directions</b>
                      <li>Get on to Voortrekker Road, and continue on this road until you merge onto the R45</li>
                      <li>Get onto N7/R45 toward Moorreesburg/Vredenburg</li>
                      <li>Follow N7 to R393 (After approximately 62km, you will encounter a roundabout - take the second exit to stay on the N7 for another 44km).</li>
                      <li>Turn right onto the R393. After 800m, turn right again. </li>
                      <li>After another 8.4km, turn right. Your destination will be in front of you 500m later.</li>
                    </ul>
                  {{/if}}

                  <li {{action (mut showWellingDirections) (not showWellingDirections)}}><b>Wellington:</b> Between 1h50min and 2h00 (We recommend 2h15min to be safe) - <i class="link">{{if showWellingDirections 'hide' 'show'}} directions</i></li>
                  {{#if showWellingDirections}}
