                      <b>Directions</b>
                      <li>Take Hoofweg Rd to Hermon Rd/R44</li>
                      <li>Turn right onto Hermon Rd/R44</li>
                      <li>Turn left onto R46</li>
                      <li>Turn right onto Church Rd/R311 (continue for 32.2km)</li>
                      <li>Turn right onto N7</li>
                      <li>Follow N7 to R393 (After approximately 31.8km, you will encounter a roundabout - take the second exit to stay on the N7 for another 44km).</li>
                      <li>Turn right onto the R393. After 800m, turn right again. </li>
                      <li>After another 8.4km, turn right. Your destination will be in front of you 500m later.</li>
                    </ul>
                  {{/if}}

                </ul>
              </div>
          {{/if}}
